            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-952789441" class="vote-count">26</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-952789441" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="952789441">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/belindali/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-23</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">满眼是吃大闸蟹，新做头发，如此长的叙事时间讲述的全是对生活的庸俗理解，浪费读者时间。把那些做作的表面材料全部捻到一起讲，显得“上海”如何如何。所谓海派的下下品</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="782911854">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-782911854" class="vote-count">40</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-782911854" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="782911854">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Orpheus/">旧精魂樟櫆枝杈</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar20 rating" title="较差"></span>
                    <span>2014-03-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">读了溢美评论，找来翻翻，释卷长叹人之有幸有不幸：韩仁均老师（韩寒爸爸），金宇澄老师，同样的二三流海派文人，同样的矫情、煽情、轻薄，一个自感不遇而藏在小儿后面作伪，为天下笑；一个却华丽转身老克剌，获得评论界追捧。时乎，境乎，黄浦江船号之悲凉乎。阿嚏。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
